    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      TipMate does not automatically collect, store, or track personally identifiable
      information. Any information you choose to provide (such as contacting us by email)
      is voluntary.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>
      Information provided by users is used solely to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to support inquiries</li>
      <li>Provide assistance related to app functionality</li>
      <li>Improve the user experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      TipMate does not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      TipMate may rely on standard third-party technologies required for app operation
      or distribution. These third-party services operate under their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      TipMate is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly
      collect personal information from children.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be posted
      on this page with an updated effective date.
